---
title: Seared Salmon & Bengali Curry Sauce with Bombay Baby Potatoes & Roast Cauliflower Toss
description: Flavour is bursting out the seams in seared salmon and roast potatoes and cauliflower. A Bengali coconut sauce makes a perfect
and delicious addition to fresh salmon and the potatoes are roasted with mustard seeds, everything is stitched together with
roasted cauliflower in the salad. It’s a masterpiece!
